title: What historical events happened in 1513? - Quora

response.answer_text: A lot of key historical events happened in 1513. It was a pretty big year for European explorers. Some of the biggest events of the year: Juan Ponce de León, the Spanish explorer, first sighted Florida.In the Battle of Novara, the Swiss Confederacy defeated the French.Vasco Nunez de Balboa, another Spanish explorer, crossed Panama and became the first European to see the Pacific Ocean.
